<ul class="gcf-lyt-detail__tags-body sorting-list sorting-list--sdg">
<li><a href="/gcf/project/sdgs/1082" class="sorting-list__item"><img srcset="/gcf/images_cf/sdg/sdg_icon_3.png 1x, /gcf/images_cf/sdg/sdg_icon_3@2x.png 2x" src="/gcf/images_cf/sdg/sdg_icon_3.png" alt="SDGアイコン" decoding="async" />3.すべての人に健康と福祉を</a></li><li><a href="/gcf/project/sdgs/1095" class="sorting-list__item"><img srcset="/gcf/images_cf/sdg/sdg_icon_16.png 1x, /gcf/images_cf/sdg/sdg_icon_16@2x.png 2x" src="/gcf/images_cf/sdg/sdg_icon_16.png" alt="SDGアイコン" decoding="async" />16.平和と公正をすべての人に</a></li>
